colonial goose
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a stuffed leg of mutton, orig. a leg of mutton boned and stuffed; now often mutton flap etc., rolled and stuffed.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
